            <title><![CDATA[【放下小手！#经常揉眼会导致结膜炎#[晕][晕][晕]】#揉眼睛会加速眼部皮肤衰老# 医务人员介绍，经常揉眼会造成眼部的感染，比如细菌性结膜炎、病毒性结膜炎。另...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【放下小手！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%8F%89%E7%9C%BC%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%86%9C%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%8F%89%E7%9C%BC%E4%BC%9A%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%BB%93%E8%86%9C%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常揉眼会导致结膜炎#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[晕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yun-3ca5d0a5b7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[晕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yun-3ca5d0a5b7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[晕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yun-3ca5d0a5b7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8F%89%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E7%9C%BC%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E8%A1%B0%E8%80%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8F%89%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E7%9C%BC%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E8%A1%B0%E8%80%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#揉眼睛会加速眼部皮肤衰老#</span></a> 医务人员介绍，经常揉眼会造成眼部的感染，比如细菌性结膜炎、病毒性结膜炎。另外，经常揉眼还会直接把角膜的细胞给摩擦掉，一些严重的患者损伤了细胞之后会造成一些炎症。细胞因子释放会造成角膜的持续炎症和溶解变薄，最终个别患者还可能发展为致盲性的圆锥角膜。此外，经常性揉眼睛也会导致眼周肌肤松弛，加速眼部皮肤衰老。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6NfQ3iG" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
